RttiPackage - Annotation Type in com.promis.rtti.annotations
Use to specify packages that hold RttiObjects Create package-info.java for required package like this:
@RttiPackage
package com.some.data.package;

import com.promis.rtti.annotations.RttiPackage;
 Subsequently all classes of this package will be probed and descendants of RttiObject or classes identified by GenerateRtti will get RTTI.
